{
  "stem": "15115.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he says to me, El, come with me back to Greece.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whatever I find, I'll give you half, which at the time, he could say anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you know something, you know, he talked me into it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was ready in Bari.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I went to Bari to get the boat to go to Athens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, [INAUDIBLE], I says, you know, sometimes I'm very-- I can tell something is wrong, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I says to him, Harry, you know something?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See how things are.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If things are OK, you let me know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can take next boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I took my suitcase.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went back to Santa Maria die Bagni.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He went back to Greece.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he found my brother alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my brother sends me a telegram and says El, don't come to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Don't come to Greece.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's rough here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Try to go to Israel or the States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the end of Greece for me, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I didn't-- I had no intentions to go back to Greece whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in Feldafing, I was-- l was like a king.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Til June, 1948.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed all the time in Feldafing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then I went to-- what do you call-- to come to Canada.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to [INAUDIBLE], a quarantine hotel to go through-- through what do you call-- through papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I made the-- the funny thing was that in 1946, I wanted to go to the States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Canada didn't exist at the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no transfer for Canada.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were sending a lot of kids under 18 to United States, because, you know, because Canada, I really didn't know too much about Canada.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
